        <div class="msgSubject">MondesPersistants: A Brief Discussion of Guild Wars 2 PvP</div>
        <div class="sm notbold">
          
          Posted: 2010-11-17 04:30:04 | Edited: Nov 19 2010 11:52am  | <input type="checkbox" name="quote-128998980462424968" id="quote-128998980462424968" class="msgQuoteCheck" onchange="multiQuote2()"/><label for="quote-128998980462424968" onclick="multiQuote2()"> Quote</label>  | <a href="/forum.html?forum=226&amp;mid=128998980462424968&amp;post=1&amp;replyto=128998980462424968&amp;page=1" class="icon-replytothis" rel="nofollow">Reply to Post</a> | <a id="FOLLOW_MID_128998980462424968" onclick="followToggle('add','128998980462424968')" href="javascript:" class="icon-follow">Follow</a> 
